Why turning on your notifications?


Notifications keep you updated about what's going on with your accounts and give you important information.


Benefits


  •  Follow all your accounts at a glance
  •  Get notified when it is pay day and for any cash credit
  •  Get notified when there are suspicious transactions
  •  Receive tailored recommendations when you can reduce your bank fees, renegotiate your mortgage, etc.

And also


You can also set up these notifications with defined amounts so they are tailored to the information you need.

If you have any questions, feel free to contact us here "
